Home > Products and Services > Forestry and Forest Products








From healthy forests to world-class forest products
At J.D. Irving, Limited (JDI), we are committed to ongoing investment in trees, in skilled people and the best technology, ensuring our forest products are world-class. Sustainability is deeply embedded in JDI's business. It's the key to creating long-term value for our customers, safeguarding the environment, providing secure employment to thousands of men and women, and delivering economic benefits to the communities where our operations are located.JDI's Forestry & Forest Product companies include:Irving WoodlandsIrving Pulp & PaperIrving PaperIrving TissueLake Utopia Corrugating MediumIrving Lumber & Value-Added Products







Irving WoodlandsIrving Woodlands is focused on rigorous land management and responsible stewardship, guided by a 100-year Management Plan that preserves the environmental and ecological integrity of our land, air, water and wildlife. 




Irving Pulp & PaperIrving Pulp & Paper produces softwood and hardwood grades of kraft pulp. We specialize in fibre for premium tissue products in global markets, producing exceptional tissue quality NBSK pulp.




Irving PaperUsing the latest technology in paper making and providing world class customer service, Irving Paper produces a wide range of products for your commercial printing needs.




Irving TissueIrving Tissue produces quality parent rolls of tissue, providing the strength and softness that have made our leading consumer and private label brands the choice of customers throughout North America.




Lake Utopia PaperLake Utopia Paper produces high quality corrugating medium for the global market, delivering world class quality and service in the production of packaging material for some of the world's favourite brands.
  




Irving Lumber & Value Added ProductsFor over 130 years, our customers have appreciated JDI's commitment to quality lumber products, strong relationships, service reliability and responsible forest management.





 




















